   "source": [
    "# Hi-C features like Virtual4C, DiScore, InsuScore\n",
    "\n",
    "Virual4C track is for mimic 4C data track from Hi-C contact matrix.\n",
    "\n",
    "DiScore and InsuScore represents the interaction bias between TAD and non-TAD regions."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import coolbox\n",
    "from coolbox.api import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "'0.2.6'"
     },
     "execution_count": 14,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "coolbox.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "<Figure size 1133.86x1526.74 with 46 Axes>",
      "image/png": "\n"
     },
     "execution_count": 15,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "example_cool = \"../../../tests/test_data/cool_chr9_4000000_6000000.mcool\"\n",
    "test_region = \"chr9:4000000-6000000\"\n",
    "\n",
    "cool_track = Cool(example_cool, style=\"matrix\")\n",
    "\n",
    "loci = [\"chr9:4380000-4380000\", \"chr9:4760000-4760000\", \"chr9:5445000-5445000\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "frame = XAxis() \\\n",
    "        + DiScore(cool_track) + Title(\"Di score\") + Spacer(0.2) \\\n",
    "        + InsuScore(cool_track, window_size=\"20-60\", style=\"heatmap\") + Title(\"IS window_size=20-60\") + Spacer(0.2) \\\n",
    "        + InsuScore(cool_track) + Title(\"IS window_size=20\") + Spacer(0.2) \\\n",
    "        + cool_track + Spacer(0.5)\n",
    "for l in loci:\n",
    "    track = Virtual4C(cool_track, l, bin_width=5) + MinValue(0) + Title(\"Virtual 4C\")\n",
    "    track +=  MaxValue(0.015)\n",
    "    frame += track + Spacer(0.5)\n",
    "frame *= Vlines(loci)\n",
    "\n",
    "frame.plot(test_region)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### CLI code"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 16,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "\n",
    "cool_file=../../../tests/test_data/cool_chr9_4000000_6000000.mcool\n",
    "loci1=\"chr9:4380000-4380000\"\n",
    "loci2=\"chr9:4760000-4760000\"\n",
    "loci3=\"chr9:5445000-5445000\"\n",
    "\n",
    "coolbox add XAxis - \\\n",
    "    add DiScore ${cool_file} - \\\n",
    "    add InsuScore ${cool_file} --window_size 20-60 --style heatmap - \\\n",
    "    add InsuScore ${cool_file} - \\\n",
    "    start_with Vlines \"['${loci1}', '${loci2}', '${loci3}']\" - \\\n",
    "    add Cool ${cool_file} --style \"matrix\" - \\\n",
    "    start_with MaxValue \"0.015\" - \\\n",
    "    start_with MinValue \"0\" - \\\n",
    "    add Virtual4C ${cool_file} \"${loci1}\" --bin_width 5 - \\\n",
    "    add Virtual4C ${cool_file} \"${loci2}\" --bin_width 5 - \\\n",
    "    add Virtual4C ${cool_file} \"${loci3}\" --bin_width 5 - \\\n",
    "    goto \"chr9:4000000-6000000\" - \\\n",
    "    plot /tmp/test_cli_hicfeature.png"
   ]
  }
 ],
